    class AppLowerToolBar
extends javafx.scene.control.ToolBar
    Implementaion of the AppLowerToolBar. This contains actually a zoom combo box, a progress bar and a language combo box.

      • setZoom

        public void setZoom(int nZoom)
        External access to the zoom value.
        Parameters:
        nZoom - An int containing the zoom value. Which shall be one of 500, 400, 300, 200, 150, 100, 75, 50, 25, 10. Where 100 means 100%.
